6.1 - The system shall support the ability to open, close, read only, reopen and respond to queries based on user roles.
6.2 - The system shall support the ability to filter queries based on records, fields, events and users.
6.3 - The system shall support the ability to attach files to queries and make them available to download based on user roles. 
6.4 - The system shall support the ability to email and send messages via REDCap messenger with a link to queries based on user roles.
6.5 - The system shall have the ability to highlight open, closed and responded to queries. 
6.6 - The system shall have the ability to verify and de-verify data value depending on user rights.
6.7 - The system shall have the ability to accept User comments for fields.
6.8 - The system shall have the ability to filter user comments based on Records, Events, Fields, Users and Keywords.